<h2 class="pdoc-module-header" id="RemoteStateReference">
<a class="pdoc-member-name" href="https://github.com/pulumi/pulumi-terraform/blob/321ad3fc507e0e95a318cab3cfdcc92796c5c826/sdk/nodejs/state/remoteStateReference.ts#L51">class <b>RemoteStateReference</b></a>
</h2>
<div class="pdoc-module-contents">
<pre class="highlight"><span class='kd'>extends</span> <a href='/reference/pkg/nodejs/pulumi/pulumi/#CustomResource'>CustomResource</a></pre>
{{% md %}}

Manages a reference to a Terraform Remote State.. The root outputs of the remote state are available
via the `outputs` property or the `getOutput` method.

{{% /md %}}
